## 7. Underlying Price Signal Dataset

```
tick_dataset (Arrow IPC, 1GB hugepage):
  tick_id          uint64    tick number (0 to 999,999)
  fair_value       float64   reference price (e.g. $1500.25)
  volatility       float64   realized vol — drives MM quote width
  tick_size        float64   minimum increment
  news_flag        uint8     0=normal, 1=event (bots trade aggressively)

Pre-recorded per round. Same price journey for all contestants.
Bot REACTIONS differ per contestant (because their LOBs evolve differently).
This is FAIR: a better algo should produce better outcomes vs the SAME bots.
```

