## 8. Scoring System

```
Primary Score:    Final PnL% = (cash + position×last_price - capital) / capital × 100
Tiebreaker:       Avg ns/tick (lower = better, only when PnL diff < 0.001%)

Penalties:
  Position limit breach    → -10% PnL per violation
  TLE tick (>100µs)        → order treated as HOLD, tick still counted
  Negative final PnL       → ranked below all positive PnL contestants

Leaderboard update:  every 1000 ticks (HDR histogram, <1ms latency)
Final score locked:  at tick 1,000,000
```

